name: Hipnotic
description:
We're in a cage, We're all living slaves,
The devil got us working day by day just to get paid,
Sometimes I think back, Relapse,
Who created hip-hop and rap? Yea,
Who's the first one that grabbed the mic?
Who's the first one that said that they'll rock the mic?
Who was the first one that swung when there was a fight?
Who's the one who brought hip-hop alive?
Who's the first one who said later hip-hop would die?
Who's the one brought the bass, snares and vibes?
Yea, rock the vibes,
Hip-hop underground knocks the sound,
Low-Key, Ground and Pound, Winning every round,
Spreading out everywhere throughout the town,
Yea, throughout the town.

The devil got us working day by day,
We are wasting our lives trying to get paid,
That's why they call life a pursuit of happiness,
I'm trying to live the star life, But it hasn't happened yet,
I've been thinking about it, Patiently waiting,
Realized if you want something, 
You got to go out and get it,
Yea, I said it and I meant it,
Don't sit around senseless,
You gotta keep a conscious mindset, Never Reckless,
Stay in the clear, To reach the Devine,
The truth is there, You just gotta see the signs,
If you don't understand, Hit rewind.
